'But it is worth SOMETHING' you may think.  'The floor is $25!!, we are providing value!!' you say.  

No.  No one will take the time or make the effort to list the NFT equivalent of spam.

The hidden wallet is a place of deep shame.  No one wants to look in there, least of all me.  As a brand, if you are creating something that fires directly into my trash, you are telling me that what you are sending me is trash.  No one wants that.

My hidden wallet contains tributes to my poor judgment and awful decision making.  If a projects NFT has found its way to my hidden wallet, chances are they've done something terribly wrong.  It is my NFT garbage bin.  My own personal dumpster fire.
